ss=\"pagi\">\n<div class=\"pagi-left\">\n<a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/jobs/18/01-29-nec-researcher-data-science.html\" rel=\"prev\"><img height=\"10\" src=\"/images/prv.gif\" width=\"8\"> <strong>Previous post</strong></img></a></div>\n<div class=\"pagi-right\">\n<a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/2018/01/insurancenexus-webinar-ai-machine-learning-chatbots.html\" rel=\"next\"><strong>Next post</strong> <img height=\"10\" src=\"/images/nxt.gif\" width=\"8\"/></a></div>\n<br/>\u00a0<br/>\u00a0\n    <div class=\"addthis_native_toolbox\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tag-data\">Tags: <a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/tag/career\" rel=\"tag\">Career</a>, <a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/tag/data-scientist\" rel=\"tag\">Data Scientist</a>, <a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/tag/glassdoor\" rel=\"tag\">Glassdoor</a>, <a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/tag/jobs\" rel=\"tag\">Jobs</a>, <a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/tag/trends\" rel=\"tag\">Trends</a></div>\n<br/>\n<p class=\"excerpt\">\n     For the third year in a row, Data Scientist was ranked as the no. 1 job in America by Glassdoor.  </p>\n</div>\n<div id=\"post-header-ad\">\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">kda_sid_write(1); kda_sid_n=2;</script>\n</div>\n<hr class=\"grey-line\"/><br/>\n<div class=\"post\" id=\"post-\">\n<div class=\"author-link\"><b>By <a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/author/gregory-piatetsky\" rel=\"author\" title=\"Posts by Gregory Piatetsky\">Gregory Piatetsky</a>, KDnuggets.</b></div>  \n\nGlassdoor, a popular job site, again published a list of  \r\n<a href=\"https://www.glassdoor.com/List/Best-Jobs-in-America-LST_KQ0,20.htm\"><b>50 Best Jobs in America</b></a>, \r\nand in 2018, for the third year in a row, Data Scientist ranked as \r\nthe no. 1 job.  Data Scientist had an overall Job score 4.8 out of 5,\r\n$110,000 Median Base Salary, and over 4,000 job openings on Glassdoor.\r\n<br/><br/>\n<img alt=\"Glassdoor Data Scientist N1 Job 2018\" src=\"/images/glassdoor-data-scientist-n1-job-2018-567.jpg\" width=\"90%\"/>\n<br/><br/>\r\nIn 2017,\r\n<a href=\"/2017/01/glassdoor-data-scientist-best-job-america.html\" target=\"_blank\">\r\nGlassdoor also ranked Data Scientist as the best job in America</a>,\r\nwith the same job score and the same median base salary, but slightly higher job satisfaction. \r\nIn 2016, \r\n<a href=\"/2016/01/glassdoor-data-scientist-best-job-america.html\" target=\"_blank\">\r\nGlassdoor ranked Data Scientist as no. 1 job in USA</a> for the first time, with median salary $117K, and about 1,700 jobs listed. \r\n<br/><br/>\r\nHere are the top 5 jobs in 2018 and also other jobs in top 50 related to Analytics, Big Data, Data Science, according to Glassdoor:\r\n<br/><br/>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"2\" class=\"wc\" width=\"90%\">\n<tr class=\"wch\"><th>2018 Rank</th><th>Job Title</th><th>Job<br/>Score</th><th>Job<br/>Satisfaction</th><th>Median<br/>Base Salary</th><th>Job<br/>Openings</th>\n</tr>\n<tr><td>1</td><td>Data Scientist</td><td>4.8</td><td>4.2</td><td>$110,000</td><td>4,524</td></tr>\n<tr><td>2</td><td>DevOps Engineer</td><td>4.6</td><td>4.0</td><td>$105,000</td><td>3,369</td></tr>\n<tr><td>3</td><td>Marketing Manager</td><td>4.6</td><td>4.0</td><td>$85,000</td><td>6,439</td></tr>\n<tr><td>4</td><td>Occupational Therapist</td><td>4.5</td><td>4.0</td><td>$74,000</td><td>11,903</td></tr>\n<tr><td>5</td><td>HR Manager</td><td>4.5</td><td>3.9</td><td>$85,000</td><td>4,458</td></tr>\n<tr><td>18</td><td>Analytics Manager</td><td>4.4</td><td>3.9</td><td>$115,000</td><td>1,381</td></tr>\n<tr><td>26</td><td>Database Administrator</td><td>4.3</td><td>3.8</td><td>$94,000</td><td>2,370</td></tr>\n<tr><td>33</td><td>Data Engineer</td><td>4.2</td><td>3.7</td><td>$100,000</td><td>2,816</td></tr>\n<tr><td>38</td><td>Data Analyst</td><td>4.2</td><td>3.9</td><td>$60,000</td><td>4,729</td></tr>\n</table>\n<br/><br/>\r\nCompared to 2017 ranking, \r\nData Engineer dropped from n. 3 to n. 33, \r\nAnalytics Manager dropped from n. 5 to n. 18, and \r\nDatabase Administrator dropped from n. 7 to n. 26.\r\n<br/><br/>\r\nPerhaps the decline in job satisfaction across the number of jobs in reflected in growing demand for the job of Occupational Therapist, which jumped from n. 12 to n. 4 job in 2018?\r\n<br/><br/>\r\nNote that Data Scientist and Machine Learning engineer were also\r\n<a href=\"/2017/12/linkedin-machine-learning-data-scientist-top-jobs.html\" target=\"_blank\">\r\ntop US emerging jobs</a>, according to LinkedIn.\r\n<br/><br/>\r\nYou can also reach those talented but hard-to-find Data Scientists and Machine Learning Engineers by placing a \r\n<a href=\"/jobs/\" target=\"_blank\">\r\njob ad on KDnuggets</a> - email to \r\n<b><a href=\"mailto:jobs@kdnuggets.com\" onmouseover=\"this.href='mai' + 'lto:' + 'job' + 's@' + 'kdnuggets.com'\"><img align=\"top\" alt=\"jobs\" border=\"0\" height=\"26\" src=\"/images/jobs-kd.jpg\" width=\"174\"/></a></b>.\r\nSee <a href=\"/jobs/details.html\">Details and posting info</a>.\r\n<br/><br/>\n<b>Related:</b>\n<ul class=\"three_ul\">\n<li><a href=\"/2017/12/linkedin-machine-learning-data-scientist-top-jobs.html\">Machine Learning Engineer, Data Scientist - top US emerging jobs</a>\n<li><a href=\"/2017/01/glassdoor-data-scientist-best-job-america.html\" target=\"_blank\">Data Scientist - best job in America in 2017</a>\n<li><a href=\"/2016/01/glassdoor-data-scientist-best-job-america.html\">Data Scientist - best job in America in 2016</a>\n</li></li></li></ul> </div>\n<div class=\"page-link\"></div>\n<div class=\"pagi\">\n<hr class=\"grey-line\"/>\n<div class=\"pagi-left\">\n<a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/jobs/18/01-29-nec-researcher-data-science.html\" rel=\"prev\"><img height=\"10\" src=\"/images/prv.gif\" width=\"8\"> <strong>Previous post</strong></img></a></div>\n<div class=\"pagi-right\">\n<a href=\"https://www.kdnuggets.com/2018/01/insurancenexus-webinar-ai-machine-learning-chatbots.html\" rel=\"next\"><strong>Next 